OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny residual
OL,6,Flight showers across the Peak District
OL,7,Fwill fade to leave generally dry
OL,8,Fconditions with partly cloudy skies.
OL,9,FWinds easing to become light inland
OL,10,Fbut still breezier along the coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FGenerally dry with bright
OL,13,Fspells, although rather cloudier at
OL,14,Ftimes. Some longer sunny spells likely
OL,15,Fto develop later in the day. Light
OL,16,Fwinds inland, a little breezier along
OL,17,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
