OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FMonday, bright but turning cloudy
OL,7,Flater with some showery rain possible.
OL,8,FBreezier and often cloudier Tuesday
OL,9,Fand Wednesday, with some outbreaks of
OL,10,Frain likely at times, but gradually
OL,11,Fturning warmer.
